model

Class Profile

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.Profile
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Admin, User

    public abstract class Profile
extends java.lang.Object
    Abstract class representing a user profile in the system. Serves as the base class for different types of user profiles and defines common properties and behaviors for all profiles.
